title: Winspace Hyper X Wheel Teardown
content:
The best in class winspace wheels get a new set of bearings. This video shows how you do it. Things you will need: 6803 Bearing x 5 NTN Recommended 6903 Bearing x 1 NTN Recommended6803 Overaxle Press c9 QTY 26903 Overaxle Press c9 QTY 2
